<L>__{interior other kitchen night}
<A>__{coraline enters to see her mother cooking at the stove, wearing an apron and rooster head oven mitts. the light and colors are much warmer and the details more perfect in this kitchen. other mother is facing away from coraline as she works.}
<C>__{coraline}
<D>__{mom?! what are you doing here in the middle of the night?}
<A>__{her mother turns from the stove to greet her and coraline is dumbstruck: she's got buttons for eyes! she beams with happiness at coraline's arrival.}
